## The Perfect Setting for Your Group

Bear Lake Camp offers several off-season programs facilitated by our resident staff. Our annual Defrost and Recharge retreats for students have become a favorite for many campers and students a chance to engage Scripture, explore spiritual disciplines, re-orient their Christian life during the winter months, and have fun building relationships and playing together. Our retreats offer:

- Engaging and challenging teaching rooted in Scripture and reinforced through group discussion and personal practice
- Awesome games (camp favorites and new options)
- More relaxed pace than summer camp schedule
- Beautiful snow-covered views of Bear Lake from the Dining Hall porch

