## Defrost Winter Retreat

Defrost is our annual winter retreat for high school students. Get away from the busyness of life and experience Christ through worship, teaching, and community in a cozy winter setting.

- Dynamic worship and engaging teaching
- Snow activities and winter fun
- Small group discussions
- Warm fellowship by the fire

