## Recharge Retreat

Recharge is our annual winter retreat for Jr. High students designed to give fresh energy to their faith journeys. Step away from the everyday and reconnect with God in the beauty of Bear Lake.

- Inspiring worship and Bible teaching
- Snow play and gym activities
- Delicious meals and snacks
- Time for recharge your faith

