## Spiritual Formation Retreats

A developing vision at BLC is to offer regular retreats that focus on teaching and equipping participants in the tools that have been practiced by Christians for millennia- often called Spiritual Disciplines or Practices. These retreats will be designed to offer clear teaching and guided exercises in a specific practice.

Structured around times of individual personal retreat, we recommend these retreats for 18-65 year old participants. No one is too old or young to grow in their communion with the Lord, but we also acknowledge that our facility requires mobility and these retreats will be ideal for individuals who have completed high school.

Retreats will be offered 2x a year:

- **Fall**: Oct or Nov
- **Spring:** March or April

